title: Flu Vaccine for Children & Flu Shot Side Effects
description: Learn about the new  flu vaccination nasal spray and any side effects that are associated with the flu vaccine. Camille Sabella, MD, a doctor who treats pediatric infectious diseases at Cleveland Clinic, says that some kids now have the option of avoiding a flu shot altogether.
